      "content": "but that's the thing, it doesn't feel temporary. it feels like the end of the road. everything i built is gone and there's no coming back from this kind of failure in my circle. when you look at the math of the debt and the ruined reputation, it feels like the only way to stop the crushing weight of the shame is to just... stop. to just not have to face the next morning. if i'm not the provider and the success, then what's even the point of carrying this around?",
